{
  "stem": "1338.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Judenrat, certainly I would not want to get involved at this point of discussing what the role of Chaim Rumkowski was, which was the Jewish King of Lodz Ghetto which many books and movies were made about.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think it's controversial to this very day what he did and how he did it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyway, a lot of people were falling prey to it because they didn't have a connection.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't get a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was somebody who made and placed them, and they were strangers in town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A tragic, for example, was the story of the Prague and Viennese and the other Jews that were brought from Germany and herded into the Jewish-- into the Lodz Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these people were completely out of touch with the rest of the population, and they fell prey to both hunger, deprivation, and eventually deportations.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing was obvious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nothing was simple.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was-- any statement I am making is not inclusive, it's just statistically indicative of the times and of what was happening.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my life was continued until '41 when the schooling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father refused to work, and then he finally went to-- see, he's got-- he knew all these guys in the lumber business.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So all he had to go and to talk to some of these guys who were running the lumberyard factory or whatever it was for furniture that was done that was going on in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he didn't-- he was very hard, had a lot of quarrels with him on that subject.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Today I regret it very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Today I think he was right.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
